About this item

Product details

Keeping it all together with Reebok’s Bobbie Top Loader Backpack. A spacious carry-all that’s the perfect size for all your essentials, even your laptop, and features adjustable, padded straps for a comfortable fit. An ideal choice for the classroom, a hike or running around town, this is a must-have in any season.
  • Material: 100% Polyester     
    • Care: Wipe clean
    • Country of Origin: Imported
    • Exterior Dimensions: 13.5” W x 18.75” H x 7.25” D. Width is measured across the bottom of the backpack.
    • Exterior Features: Top loading with zipper closure; side mesh pockets; padded, adjustable straps with backpack clips; padded mesh top carry handle; sunglass pocket; front zipper compartment; reflective tape; logo patch
    • Interior Features: Spacious compartments; jersey-lined storage sleeve for laptops; zipper pocket
